{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/instagram1","webpackCompilationHash":"b58cd8ff0292e0704fac","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"10e0f6b1-e52e-5d1e-b9dc-d4d9babc9dc0","html":"<h2 id=\"instagram-페이지-copy-하기\"><a href=\"#instagram-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80-copy-%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"instagram 페이지 copy 하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Instagram 페이지 copy 하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-로그인-페이지-구현-\"><a href=\"#1-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84-\" aria-label=\"1 로그인 페이지 구현  permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 로그인 페이지 구현 ​</h3>\n<p>HTML,CSS,JavaScript 를 이용하여<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 732px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/edad24b909ecb683aa301b132dc34550/7ec06/login.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 108.19672131147541%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/edad24b909ecb683aa301b132dc34550/01472/login.webp 240w,\n/static/edad24b909ecb683aa301b132dc34550/222bd/login.webp 480w,\n/static/edad24b909ecb683aa301b132dc34550/7dd13/login.webp 732w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 732px) 100vw, 732px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/edad24b909ecb683aa301b132dc34550/0783d/login.png 240w,\n/static/edad24b909ecb683aa301b132dc34550/782f4/login.png 480w,\n/static/edad24b909ecb683aa301b132dc34550/7ec06/login.png 732w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 732px) 100vw, 732px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/edad24b909ecb683aa301b132dc34550/7ec06/login.png\"\n          alt=\"login\"\n          title=\"login\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span> </p>\n<p>위와 같은 로그인 페이지를 만드는 것이다.</p>\n<p><strong>HTML 코드는 다음과 같다.</strong>\n<code></p>\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"common.css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"login.css\">\n    <title>repl.it</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    \n    <div class=wrapper>\n        <div class=content1>\n            <img src=\"logo_text.png\" alt=\"\">\n            <div id=\"box1\"><input type=\" text\" class=\"phone\" placeholder=\"전화번호, 사용자 이름 또는 이메일\"></div>\n            <div id=\"box2\"><input type=\" text\" class=\"password\" placeholder=\"비밀번호\"></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">        &lt;button id=&quot;login&quot; onclick=&quot;alert(&#39;로그인성공&#39;)&quot; &gt;\n            로그인\n        &lt;/button&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n    &lt;div class=&quot;bottom&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;p class=&quot;passwordtext&quot;&gt;비밀번호를 잊으셨나요? &lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre></div>\n</body>\n<script src=\"login.js\"></script>\n</html>\n</code>\n<p><strong>CSS 코드는 다음과 같다.</strong></p>\n<code>\nbody {\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    background: #fafafa;\n}\n<p>.wrapper {\nmax-width: 350px;\nheight: 380px;\nborder: 1px solid #e6e6e6;\nbackground: #fff;\nmargin: 60px auto;\n}</p>\n<p>img {\nmax-width: 175px;\nheight: 51px;\ndisplay: block;\nwhite-space: nowrap;\ntext-indent: 110%;\nmargin: 22px auto 12px;</p>\n<p>}</p>\n<p>.phone,\n.password {\nmargin-bottom: 5px;\ndisplay: block;\ncolor: rgba(var(—i1d, 38, 38, 38), 1);\nline-height: 18px;\nbackground: #fafafa;\nmargin: 0;\nfont-size: 14px;\nborder: 1px solid #fafafa;\nborder-radius: 3px;\npadding: 9px 0 7px 8px;\nwidth: 250px;\nheight: 20px;\n}</p>\n<h1 id=\"box1\"><a href=\"#box1\" aria-label=\"box1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>box1,</h1>\n<h1 id=\"box2-\"><a href=\"#box2-\" aria-label=\"box2  permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>box2 {</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">margin: 0 auto 4px auto;\nwidth: 266px;\nheight: 36px;\nborder: 1px solid #efefef;\nborder-radius: 3px;\npadding-bottom: 3px;</code></pre></div>\n<p>}</p>\n<h1 id=\"login-\"><a href=\"#login-\" aria-label=\"login  permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>login {</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">font-weight: bold;\ndisplay: block;\nmargin: 0 auto;\nmargin-top: 5px;\nbackground-color: #c3dffa;\ncolor: #ffffff;\nborder: 1px solid #efefef;\nborder-radius: 3px;\nwidth: 268px;\nheight: 30px;</code></pre></div>\n<p>}</p>\n<p>input {\nmargin: 0 auto;\nline-height: 18px;\nfont-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ‘Segoe UI’, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, ‘Open Sans’, ‘Helvetica Neue’, sans-serif\n}</p>\n<p>.passwordtext {\ntext-align: center;\nfont-size: 12px;\nline-height: 14px;\nmargin-top: 140px;\ncolor: #003569;</p>\n<p>}</p>\n<p>button {\nmargin: 0 auto;\nline-height: 18px;\nfont-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ‘Segoe UI’, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, ‘Open Sans’, ‘Helvetica Neue’, sans-serif\n}\n</code></p>\n<p>코드들이 정리가 안되고 반복되는 것이 많아 좋은 코드라 할 수가 없다…\n만들당시에는 정신없이 쌓아가고 있었기 때문이다…</p>\n<p>그 다음 제일 중요한 js 코드이다.</p>\n<p><strong>JavaScript 코드</strong></p>\n<code>\nconst id = document.getElementsByClassName('phone')[0];\nconst password = document.getElementsByClassName('password')[0];\nconst loginButton = document.getElementById('login');\n<p>loginButton.disabled = true;\nid.addEventListener(‘keydown’, function () {\nloginButton.disabled = true;\n})</p>\n<p>password.addEventListener(‘keydown’, function(){\nif(id.value ==”){\nloginButton.disabled = true;\n}else if(id.value || password.value){\nloginButton.disabled= false;\nloginButton.style.backgroundColor= “#3897f0”;\n}else{\nloginButton.disabled=true;\n}\n})\n</code></p>\n<p>Javascript 의 내용을 보면 ID와 비밀번호에 입력값이 있어야 로그인 버튼이 활성화되고(클릭할수있고) 색이 변한다는 것이다.</p>\n<p>4번째 줄부터 해석을 하면</p>\n<code>\nloginButton.disabled = true;\n</code>\n<ol>\n<li>로그인버튼의 비활성은 true , 즉 비활성화가 맞는 상태란 것이다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><code>id.addEventListener(‘keydown’, function () {\nloginButton.disabled = true;\n})</code></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>아이디입력칸에 keydown 이벤트가 발생하게 되면 함수가 실행된다. 그 함수의 내용에는 여전히 비활성이 true 라는 것.</li>\n</ol>\n<code>\npassword.addEventListener('keydown', function(){\n    if(id.value ==''){\n        loginButton.disabled = true;\n    }else if(id.value || password.value){\n        loginButton.disabled= false;\n        loginButton.style.backgroundColor= \"#3897f0\";\n    }else{\n        loginButton.disabled=true;\n    }\n})\n</code>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>패스워드 입력칸에 keydown 이벤트가 발생하면 함수가 실행되는데, </li>\n</ol>\n<p><code>if(id.value ==”){\nloginButton.disabled = true;</code></p>\n<p>   그 함수에는 만약 id값이 비어 있다면 여전히 로그인 버튼은 비활성이고, </p>\n   <code>\n   else if(id.value || password.value){\n        loginButton.disabled= false;\n        loginButton.style.backgroundColor= \"#3897f0\";\n    }else{\n        loginButton.disabled=true;\n    }\n})\n</code>\n<p>그렇지 않고 id의 value 값, 즉 아이디가 입력되거나 혹은 password의 value값이 있으면 로그인 버튼 비활성화는 false가 되어, 활성이 된다! 그리고, 로그인버튼의 배경색은 #3897f0 으로 변경되고!! if의 조건이 충족되지 않으면 활성이 일어나지 않는다!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 415px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7ce0b29b2da0f8e50aae3a713726bbff/c488c/mylogin.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100.2409638554217%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7ce0b29b2da0f8e50aae3a713726bbff/01472/mylogin.webp 240w,\n/static/7ce0b29b2da0f8e50aae3a713726bbff/8874e/mylogin.webp 415w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 415px) 100vw, 415px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7ce0b29b2da0f8e50aae3a713726bbff/0783d/mylogin.png 240w,\n/static/7ce0b29b2da0f8e50aae3a713726bbff/c488c/mylogin.png 415w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 415px) 100vw, 415px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/7ce0b29b2da0f8e50aae3a713726bbff/c488c/mylogin.png\"\n          alt=\"mylogin\"\n          title=\"mylogin\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그 결과 위와 같은 이미지가 완성 되었고, Javascript도 구현이 되었는데 어떻게 이곳에 올리는지는 모르겠다 … ㅠㅠ</p>\n<hr>\n<p>이렇게 Instagram 로그인 페이지 구현은 완료되었다…</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/instagram1","tagSlugs":["/tag/wecode/","/tag/wecode-첫번째-project/","/tag/위코드-부트캠프/","/tag/instagram-copy/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-10-07T22:40:32.169Z","description":"Instagram login page 구현하기","tags":["Wecode","Wecode 첫번째 project","위코드 부트캠프","instagram copy"],"title":"Wecode 2주 1일차","socialImage":"/media/image-3.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/instagram1"}}}